  "texts": [
    "Remarkably, GPT-3, 3.5, and 4 models surpass LLama models significantly.",
    "Within the GPT model family, performance significantly improves with each successive version upgrade.",
    "GPT-3-davinci, in particular, achieved the highest performance among all GPT-3 models.",
    "Interestingly, the performance of the fine-tuned GPT-3 model closely rivals that of GPT-4 though the fine-tuned GPT-3 model outperforms both the pretrained GPT-3.5 and GPT-4 models.",
    "Tables 3 and 4 show the NER performance for various entity types, encompassing investigation, nervous_AE, other_AE, procedure, social_circumstance, and temporal_expression respectively."
